{"tid":2235791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國宣布制裁18間伊朗銀行","createTime":"2020-10-09T03:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T08:23:17.000Z","uid":189046,"like":53,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4bcc13099877ec99b6729d59996b1a0d7a7d1b80","tid":2235791,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:28:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553748-20201009.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553748-20201009.htm&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr6ix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=694065ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1553748-20201009.htm&h=4700bb66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1553748-20201009.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n伊朗外長扎里夫強烈譴責美方宣布對18間伊朗銀行實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\n美國財長努欽發表聲明，表示華府需要阻止伊朗「非法使用美元」，將凍結被制裁銀行在美國境內的資產，又限制與美國民眾進行交易。扎里夫在社交網站表示，在新型肺炎疫情之下，華府企圖摧毀伊朗進口食品、藥品的支付通道，是「反人類的罪行」。<br />\n<br />\n路透社引述分析指出，華府今次對伊朗的進一步制裁，將影響部分與伊朗進行獲允許交易的歐洲國家銀行。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/pussy1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b4d45f9378c4124ab0715f7f01dbf51446a382","tid":2235791,"uid":82389,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:33:30.000Z","msg":"匯豐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70989b850ce660a16be0a4d6f4b60c0303088a4f","tid":2235791,"uid":83582,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:34:38.000Z","msg":"10.12 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855796d0f6e7ea410ba3b992f8a0971df9813f49","tid":2235791,"uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T03:35:15.000Z","msg":"侵真係捉緊一盤好大既棋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa12a8cd765967b1cb8b2906dd8d5abd31e1f79","tid":2235791,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"